Interface LogPublisherCfg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Configuration
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AccessLogPublisherCfg, CsvFileAccessLogPublisherCfg, CsvFileHTTPAccessLogPublisherCfg, DebugLogPublisherCfg, ErrorLogPublisherCfg, ExternalAccessLogPublisherCfg, ExternalHTTPAccessLogPublisherCfg, FileBasedAccessLogPublisherCfg, FileBasedAuditLogPublisherCfg, FileBasedDebugLogPublisherCfg, FileBasedErrorLogPublisherCfg, FileBasedHTTPAccessLogPublisherCfg, HTTPAccessLogPublisherCfg, JsonFileAccessLogPublisherCfg, JsonFileHTTPAccessLogPublisherCfg

    public interface LogPublisherCfg
extends Configuration
    A server-side interface for querying Log Publisher settings.

    Log Publishers are responsible for distributing log messages from different loggers to a destination.
